      <odd id="aspace_475afab4aaece525625e8712ca1f4368">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 4-B (YRG 4-B), Records of Yale deputy, associate, and assistant secretaries.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_3a3afae39adee41ff25075ff1121a84d">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of the Secretary, 1982.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <prefercite id="aspace_5962f9af086299053ff29d324d41cee4">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Lawrence M. Noble, Associate Secretary, Yale University, Records Concerning the Athletic Association (RU 67). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a9505b2c16c6b36f57fae8ec81bc73f4">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_3f8bd3c3dc683a7655201fdf5b89f437">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, complaints, budget materials, and administrative records documenting committees, coaches, sports, personnel, intercollegiate athletics, investments, real estate, facilities, and legislation concerning athletics at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_57d14ac7122ce59a71525f614deb4a4c">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to Boxes 2 and 6 are restricted.  The remainder of the collection is open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_bb804fc04adfaa95c64dc85d9199236a">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
